messages.messageBody:
Have your kids gone? Haleigh and I would love to hear about it! She'd like
to go next year. She's begging to go this year but I'm not sure how I feel
about it just yet. I've read the website front to back but I'd really like
to hear from someone who'd been there, or who's child has been anyway. :)

Jennifer
